title: ACCU-CHEK Active
details: The Accu-Chek Active Glucose Monitor is an easy to use system that comprises powerful features like accurate blood glucose measurement, pre-and post-meal reminders, visual double-check and two-button intuitive handling and is suitable for self-testing.

title: Novofine Pen Needle
details: Novofine needles are insulin needles available in 6 mm 32 gauge, 6 mm 31 gauge, and 8 mm 30 gauge designs.These needles are used to deliver insulin directly into the layer of fat below the skin.

title: Rossmax Thermometer
details: Rossmax Digital Thermometer TG100 is a medical device designed for accurate and easy temperature measurement. It is used to measure body temperature in both adults and children, providing a quick and reliable reading. This type of digital thermometer is commonly used for monitoring fever and general health.

title: Tens Therapy Machine
details: Transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation (TENS) is a method of pain relief involving the use of a mild electrical current. A TENS machine is a small, battery-operated device that has leads connected to sticky pads called electrodes. You attach the pads directly to your skin.

title: Match Blood Glucose 50 Test Strip
details: Easy to use Suitable for self-testing Fast and accurate results in 5 seconds Suitable with Ok Meter Match or Match II blood glucose meter
